  "rationale": "This supervisor prioritizes rapid marker acquisition and approach, robust obstacle avoidance, and safe, deterministic transitions. It uses helper states for committed actions (forward, rotate, scan, marker tracking/approach, recovery) and ensures all uncontrollable events are handled in every state. Marker_seen triggers tracking; marker_lost triggers search/scan; marker_close always leads to a terminal stop. Obstacle recovery always passes through a scan before resuming exploration, and oscillations are avoided by consistent turn preferences.",
